Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This power... It's just like Father's!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuckoo Clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a handful you are, my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those flames are blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's more powerful than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the Demon-Slaying Blade could hold it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous! Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi... e... mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. It's alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blue, no matter how I look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Arthur Auguste Angel, Upper First Class Exorcist of the Vatican Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Arthur Auguste Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the recently appointed new Paladin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Paladin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And your direct superior, Shura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Shura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't your mission to investigate and report on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what the Head of the Japanese Branch, Mephisto Pheles, and the deceased Shiro Fujimoto had been hiding together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You had other spies anyway, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... But you had another important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you can determine that that thing is related to Satan, exterminate {EXTERMINAAATE }it."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shura, don't you think that the creature clad in blue flames just a moment ago is related to Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your deductions never cease to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mephisto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a while, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you have collected the title of Paladin too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me voice my joy thereupon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally decided to show your tail?{ pun, he means "showing one's true colors" but the word sounds the same as "showing one's tail"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Council of Grigori recognizes your betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This case is the absolute proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can assure you that I am not flaunting my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insulting a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Caliburn, give me strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee~ Arthur! It'll be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the decree of the Grigori of the Highest Court of the Order of the True Cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall exterminate {EXTERMINAAATE }Satan's spawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirigakure Demon Sword Technique: Slither!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Snakefang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you protecting Satan's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you sided with Mephisto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to honor Fujimoto's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do this for the man who was the worst Paladin ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, idiot. You baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not bald. What a fascinating jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Grigori's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,New orders from the Grigori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They have decided to summon Mephisto Pheles, the Head of the Japanese Branch to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shura, you will come too as a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course the spawn of Satan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an important piece of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, I'll come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have duties towards your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be used to suppress his flames anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then shall we get going, Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We hereby commence the trial of the Head of the Japanese Branch of the Order of the True Cross, Mephisto Pheles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones questioning will be I, Timothy Timowan, head of Law Enforcement in the Order,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Paladin Arthur Auguste Angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Grigori, the High Council of the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Pheles, I will ask you up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that demon there the son of Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time for excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin Okumura was born of Satan and a human woman 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He possesses the power of Satan's blue flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you {\i1}are{\i0} his twin brother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the flames. I undergo daily checkups, but I'm just an ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that the report according to which
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the son of Satan born to Lower Second Class Exorcist Yurie Gin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,was slain with the Demon-Slaying Blade by Shiro Fujimoto was fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. One of the boys did not have Satan's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who has it is right here before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have sealed the demonic powers of this boy into the Demon-Slaying Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,About three months ago the Demon-Slaying Blade couldn't suppress his flames anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and his powers were awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then he knew nothing about all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not a demon or anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't make assumptions!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The court might sentence him to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If he succumbs to his flames, he will turn into a demon completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, they won't allow him to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Are you saying he should just die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to make him suffer even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much he wants it, he can't be a normal human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword has cracked...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kurikara cracked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know the name of this sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only called it the Demon-Slaying Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kurikara... That blade was an heirloom of our temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon, shouldn't we bring it to Yoshikuni?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshikuni?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The place where the Kurikara was forged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And can they fix it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it. I don't get it... What are you all thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared? What's this about fixing the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... Is that really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the son of Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a way to save my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Suguro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For what purpose did Fujimoto raise him in secret, Sir Pheles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To turn him into a weapon against Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Against Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't listen to that swindler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you haven't forgotten who he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Flattery like this is what they're so good at!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead us to that Yoshikuni's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else knows where it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep talking but you aren't saying anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already in Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a key to every city with a holy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lil' Ryu! Lil' Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lil' Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't put apple in it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a great cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly the demons are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is also a fact that since the ancient times
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we have learnt wisdom and countermeasures from demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we still haven't cleared Sir Pheles' charges of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sir Pheles has been a great aid to the Order
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,over the past 200 years and he has earned a certain amount of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He and Shiro Fujimoto secretly raised the son of Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an undeniable truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The 11th Yoshikuni, a descendant of the one who forged the Kurikara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,20,,A female sword-smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,25,,'s nuthin' to be suprise' 'bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,30,,{\q2}'n the middle o' the Edo Period 'ere was a\N\Nfamous sword-smith called the Female Kunishige.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,25,,'ven if 's left outta yer history books, I think she wasn't th' only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,30,,{\q2}This chick's been babbling all her life\N\Nabout how she'll be the second most famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"This chick"? Watch yer tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Bon's powerless here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My father and I oft' went to Lil' Ryu's temple fer ritual items,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so we've known each other fer ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,'e was sooo cute when 'e was lil'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,'e was clingin' t' me like a baby all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,'e even propose' to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Made me a ring outta lotus 'n stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Will ye please marry me?" 'n so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,'t ain't gonna be easy, but I think fixin' it might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To forge a Japanese-style sword like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we need jewel steel refine' in a furnace wit' bellows,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but fer a demon sword, ye need special rituals too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to forge spiritual energy into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the tradition o' that ritual has waned
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,'n there ain't anyone alive tha' still remembers it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there no records?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,'tis impossible to create new jewel steel fer demon swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We came all this way for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't make new jewel steel, what if we had some that already existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, if ye had some... But where would ye get any?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use that old nail from the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An old nail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Blue Night our whole temple burned down, including the most ancient pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only a huge nail left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But to tell the truth it's quite a treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so we entrusted it to another temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That nail was made by a Yoshikuni...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was made from the same jewel steel as the swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,'tis possible that 'tis the same jewel steel as the Kurikara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if we got that nail...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mebbe I could try fixin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, let's look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the main hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look at the crypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait here, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not dead, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine, he's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, over there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong? Don't you want to defeat Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why would you help a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look into your heart. He is the son of Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't abandoning him be better for the sake of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to help the son of Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're related?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The opponent you're scared of deep within your heart is your brother, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he's alive, you will be scared of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you trying to save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your reason for helping the son of Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your temple because of Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you help his son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Without him you could live your life in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. I'm not afraid of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm afraid of is that my strength won't be enough to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I vowed to become strong to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay it back its deeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Suguro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason? Of course I have one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd become an Exorcist to kick Satan's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he tells me why he said weird stuff like that even though he's Satan's son,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna stoop so low as to let him die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Eternal Buddha have mercy on you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The head priest is alright too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Those demons earlier were Mara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The demon who tempted Buddha when he was about to reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're demons that attack the weaknesses and uncertainties in the hearts of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not unusual that Mara possess the Buddha statues in old temples like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the nail you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mephisto was obviously deceiving the Order to overthrow it from the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's also a fact that we have nothing we can use to fight Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem of unprecedented gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If something were to go wrong, the risk is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, how long's this gonna take...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where? Where is he? I haven't lost yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What would the Earth King be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your work, Sir Pheles?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the time for joking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I need to resort to such measures?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But rather than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,why not see this as a great opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to observe the real power of Satan's offspring?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that he is the only strength we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you make this gamble with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Rin Okumura become the savior of Assiah,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or the demon king of Gehenna?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see it for yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,'s alright, I can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The time for voting is almost over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please decide whether you're for or against!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:23:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:24:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to return the favor{ settle it with you}, Rin Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
