Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.77,OP,,0,0,0,,Dark side in my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:50.36,OP,,0,0,0,,the unerasable sadness of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.57,OP,,0,0,0,,It's alright if I don't really mean it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:55.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,430)}so I fire my blasters and stretch out my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:00.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,230)}Since when has my way been unavoidable like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:04.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,400)}And now there's no one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:07.50,OP,,0,0,0,,Fuck this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.13,OP,,0,0,0,,I cry for my pride, I can't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.63,OP,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}An aria of love resounding through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:17.30,OP,,0,0,0,,this distorted reality of twisted prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.14,OP,,0,0,0,,My dreams and tomorrow are collapsing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:23.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,230)}because throwing away the lies would be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:25.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,430)}Good bye precious life.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.40,0:01:27.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Go and repaint this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.36,OP,,0,0,0,,try it for your pride, covered in wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.86,OP,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.49,OP,,0,0,0,,Even so, I sing the song of love and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:37.70,OP,,0,0,0,,let its wish reach through this distorted world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.54,OP,,0,0,0,,to build our bonds and the tomorrow to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}Throwing away the lies was important after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,430)}because this is my precious life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:50.63,OP,,0,0,0,,Dark cloud in my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.59,OP,,0,0,0,,disappearing and light is shining on the road I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.47,OP,,0,0,0,,Let's fight, there's no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:59.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,820)}I brandished my two-edged sword.
