Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(140,980)}(WIRED...)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:57.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,0)}I'm lightly fluttering in wondrous light
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:02.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,440)}like a dancing butterfly in midair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:06.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,500)}Is this place in another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:10.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(140,820)}My fall isn't slowing down so
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.67,0:22:13.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(220,480)}cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:17.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(250,0)}Cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:18.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The numbers that make my head spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:20.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,230)}are forming a rising spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:24.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}and there I notice a terrible error.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:28.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Connecting people to one another
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:31.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}is a shining pale indigo blue wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:35.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's beautiful like a thread of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:39.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder if it's what they call the chains of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:42.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:44.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:47.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:50.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:54.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}wired life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.63,0:22:58.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:22:59.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:02.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:05.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:12.15,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,900)}There is wired life.
